        "created_at": "2019-06-05T10:23:43.979Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Please check out this post: <a href=\"https://forums.foundationdb.org/t/roles-classes-matrix/1340\" class=\"inline-onebox\">Roles / Classes matrix</a><br>\nSpecifically, this section from Alex answers your query:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>DataDistribution will recruit as many storage servers as it can from processes that match Storage at Unset or better. WorstFit class processes will only be used there are no healthy storage teams left, so we need to make drastic actions to try and restore fault tolerance back to  <em>ReplicationFactor</em>  copies of data.</p>\n</blockquote>",
